From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 19:28:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(file): flock + POSIX/OFD record locks and fcntl wiring

Add inode-keyed BSD flock, byte-range record locks (F_SETLK/W, OFD, GETLK),
wait-queue blocking with EINTR/EAGAIN semantics, fd-close and process-exit
cleanup, fasync owner fields on File, and EINVAL for unknown fcntl cmds.
Also route execve/close_range/dup3 through close_file_like so locks release.

Made-with: Cursor

